## 2025-05-23 — Initial release (foundational scaffold)

- Overview: First public scaffold of EveryTool.tech with core architecture, shared UI, and initial content directories. Vanilla HTML/CSS/JS only.

### Core Architecture
- `app-loader.js` — universal loader for `header.html` and `footer.html`
- `header-search.js` + `universal-search-deploy.js` — global search with Fuse.js and polyfills
- `search-index.json` — source data for universal search
- `index.html` — landing page (hero, categories, blog carousel, FAQ hooks)
- `styles.css` — global styles (tokens-compatible)
- `view.js`, `script.js` — shared view utilities and landing scripts
- `back-to-top.js`, `back-to-top.css` — utility component
- `FAQ section/` — `faq.html`, `faq.css`, `faq.js` accordion component

### Shared Layout
- `header.html`, `footer.html` (+ `header(blog).html`, `header(backup).html`)
- Consistent placeholders and deferred script loading across pages

### Tools System
- `tools/` (category-based, standalone HTML per tool, shared `tools/tool.css`)
- Categories present from day one (examples below; not exhaustive):
  - `developer-tools/` — base64, color picker, CSS gradient, JSON formatter, regex tester, text diff, URL tools, UUID
  - `datetime-tools/` — age, business days, countdown, date duration, time calculator, work hours, timezone converter
  - `education-tools/` — assignment deadline, CGPA converter, final grade, GPA (standard and weighted), reading time, study time
  - `file-conversion-tools/` — audio converter, DOCX→PDF, Excel→CSV, PDF split/merge, SVG→PNG/JPG
  - `financial-tools/` — loan/mortgage calculators and related tools
  - `health-tools/` — set of 7 health calculators
  - `math-tools/` — set of 10 math calculators
  - `productivity-tools/` — set of 6 productivity tools
  - `seo-tools/` — set of 11 SEO tools
  - Root tools: `loan-calculator.html`, `mortgage-calculator.html`, `base64-encoder-decoder.html`, `tool.html`

### Tools Hub & Categories
- `tools-hub/` — `index.html`, `script.js`, `styles.css` (central directory + filters)
- `category-pages/` — category landing pages for date-time, developer, education, file conversion, finance, health, image/media, math, productivity, SEO, text, utility/data
- `category-pages/category(search).js` — client-side filtering

### Blog System
- `blog/` — hub (`index.html`), shared styles (`styles.css`), data loader (`script.js`)
- `blog/articals/` — `blog.html`, `blog.css`, starter article template(s)
- `blog/blog-images/` — article media

### Games Hub
- `game/` — hub (`index.html`, `styles.css`, `script.js`)
- Playable titles: 2048, Chess, Connect-Four, Minesweeper, Snake, Sudoku, Tic-Tac-Toe
- `_template/` — bootstrap template for new games

### Site Ops, SEO, and Legal
- `sitemap.xml`, `sitemap.html`, `robots.txt`
- `site.webmanifest`
- Static pages: `about.html`, `contact.html`, `privacy-policy.html`, `terms.html`, `cookie-policy.html`, `support.html`, `creators.html`, `coming-soon*.html`, `404.html`
- `google636c5a3f0b08dbba.html` — search console verification

### Assets
- `assets/` — logos (SVG/PNG), favicon, UPI SVG, and profile images

